<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ordering Canteen side UI</title>
</head>
<body style="width: 70%; margin: auto">


<h1 style="text-align:center;">Order Canteen Interface</h1>

<h3>Newly Come Orders:</h3>
<div>choose an order to confirm</div>
<div class = "container">
    <div class = "menu">
        <ul class="list-unstyled" >
            <% for(let i = 0; i < unconfirmed.length; i++){%>
                <li>
                    <%- unconfirmed[i] %>
                    <button class= "btn-default center-block">confirm</button>
                </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<hr>

<h3>Waiting Orders: Waiting</h3>
<div>choose an order to finish</div>
<div class = "container">
    <div class = "menu">
        <ul class="list-unstyled" >
            <% for(let i = 0; i < unfinished.length; i++){%>
                <li>
                    <%- unfinished[i] %>
                    <button class= "btn-default center-block">confirm</button>
                </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<hr>

<h3>Finished Orders:</h3>
<div>Once finished, send remind automaticallyï¼Œthen can send remind manually</div>
<div class = "container">
    <div class = "menu">
        <ul class="list-unstyled" >
            <% for(let i = 0; i < unfinished.length; i++){%>
                <li>
                    <%- unfinished[i] %>
                    <button class= "btn-default center-block">confirm</button>
                </li>
            <%}%>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<hr>

<div>Display coming orders</div>
<div>Update order information</div>
<div>Send reminding message</div>
</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>

